revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Floor_LowerToLowest}} {{Special|21|tag, speed|Floor|LowerToLowest}}
* ''tag'': Tag of affected sector * ''speed'': How quickly the floor moves
Lowers a tagged sector's floor to the height of the lowest surrounding floor. If ''tag'' is 0, then the sector on the line's back side is used.
== Examples ==
{{noexamples}}
